    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm on this metronidazole for a nasty tooth infection i got yesterday. i was really looking forward to a glass of red wine with dinner tonight, is it actually a big deal if i have just a little bit? like one or two glasses? won't just a tiny bit be okay?",
